      "raw_text": "Secretary Monroe of the chamber\nof commerce has been looking after\nthe interests of the Interstate fair\nduring the absence of Manager Co.'S\ngrove. Yesterday Monroe receive a\nletter from Taggard & Riggs, prom\ninent fruit growers of North Yaki-\nma, asking for a premium list and\nstating that 1t was their intention\n10 send an extensive exhibit to the\nfair. A number Of fruit growers have\nsignified their intention to send ex-\nhibits to the fair."
